        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">School Catchment Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Mansfield High catchment, established family community</p>
