    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/wishart" style="color:#c4912a;">Wishart</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carindale" style="color:#c4912a;">Carindale</a>, <a href="/suburbs/mount-gravatt-east" style="color:#c4912a;">Mount Gravatt East</a>.</p>
