<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Mansfield.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Mansfield?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">The Mansfield State High School catchment is the single most important value driver for this suburb's family buyer pool, providing a consistent floor of motivated demand that supports values across market cycles. Beyond catchment, block size and configuration, property condition, proximity to Carindale and Westfield Garden City retail, and motorway access all contribute. The combination of catchment access and practical southern corridor connectivity is what distinguishes Mansfield from surrounding suburbs at comparable distances from the CBD.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Mansfield?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Mansfield homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. Catchment-motivated buyers tend to be the most purposeful buyers in this market: they have made a clear decision about where they need to be and are actively monitoring supply within the catchment boundary. When a well-presented property appears at a realistic price, this buyer group moves efficiently. Correct pricing against current comparables is the most controllable lever for campaign speed.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Mansfield?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Mansfield offers a settled, family-oriented lifestyle about fourteen kilometres from the Brisbane CBD. The suburb's well-maintained streets, local parks, and community infrastructure reflect the stable owner-occupier character that has defined it for decades. Carindale shopping, Westfield Garden City, and the retail strip at Wishart all sit within a short drive, and the motorway corridors give residents efficient access across Brisbane and to the Gold Coast without requiring travel through heavy urban traffic.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Mansfield a good suburb to buy property in?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Mansfield offers genuine appeal for families who are prioritising the Mansfield High catchment alongside a well-established residential environment with strong surrounding amenity. The suburb's catchment-driven demand provides consistent buyer competition that supports values, and its established character, practical lot sizes, and proximity to Carindale, Wishart, and the motorway corridors make it a sound long-term family holding. Its position in the southern corridor gives it practical connectivity that more lifestyle-oriented addresses at similar distances may not match.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

